{"tid":1221260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衷心多謝黑警發哂癲，神助攻反送中，由其係前線黑警！","createTime":"2019-06-14T07:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T08:45:10.000Z","uid":188907,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a074f88e510ff1baba750f1d9cda154a4f62bca","tid":1221260,"uid":188907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"老老實實，真係好撚多謝黑警係到發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇你地打記者，阻傷者出入，扑鳩d手無寸鐵學生<br />\n邊得黎國際社會咁大肆報導<br />\n<br />\n加上個凶神惡煞ge狗樣 見人就射胡椒噴霧<br />\n仲要用埋視覺效果極佳ge催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明知一街都係cam 入到PP都要掉催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再黎EQ低到一個點，俾d議員撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公然唔佩戴委任證仲咁撚口響話一個代表哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柒成咁<br />\n仲唔係神助攻？<br />\n<br />\n仲要俾人用完即棄，俾政府割𥱊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCondom 都有用過你地班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衷心多謝你地，做狗做到咁撚冇尊嚴<br />\n全世界都笑鳩你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izedLxN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizedLxN.png&h=29157e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxgjF6q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxgjF6q.png&h=cad666f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tMTuiTa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtMTuiTa.png&h=8f44716a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y93Vese